Well first off I definitly wouldn't even attempting her until level 47+.
Second don't attempt her if you don't have 44 pet plain and simple you will
lose to her. I've fought her and the main problem with her is the fear spell
she casts your pet needs to be 44 so hopefully while you running around
thespectre cave he will last until youget back. It's good exp but it's not
something you can tell somebody how to do if you can't figure it out
chanches are you'll die if somebody else tells you.

Naeeldar
